      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a vehicle that\u2019s built to last! This car is in fair condition and has plenty of character, showing some honest wear and tear that comes with experience. It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, budget-friendly ride that\u2019s still got plenty of miles left to give. Well-loved and ready for its next journey, this car is a practical find for a savvy buyer!",
