    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the showroom. It has been meticulously cared for and is absolutely flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s in pristine, 'like-new' shape, this is the perfect find for you!",
